title: Air Zena: Harvard F jumps over 6-foot-10 teammate
text:
Updated Oct 19, 2015 at 1:31p ET 
Wearing a Michael Jordan jersey, Harvard forward Zena Edosomwan took off from inside the foul line and cleared 6-foot-10 freshman forward Balsa Dragovic (and two young fans) to throw down a powerful one-handed slam to win the dunk contest at Crimson Madness on Friday night. true A video posted by Andy Towne (@sportstowne) on Oct 16, 2015 at 4:35pm PDT 
Edosomwan averaged 4.0 points and 3.2 boards per game last season, but could have a breakout campaign for the Crimson in 2015-16.
